graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Operator[Operator Manager<br/>Go Controller]
        KubeRBACProxy[Kube-RBAC Proxy<br/>Metrics Security]
        Operator -->|secures| KubeRBACProxy
    end

    subgraph "Model Registry Instance (per CR)"
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        GRPCServer[gRPC Server Container<br/>9090/TCP gRPC]
        RESTProxy -->|forwards to| GRPCServer

        subgraph "Istio Sidecar (optional)"
            EnvoyProxy[Envoy Proxy<br/>mTLS Enforcement]
        end
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Database[(PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP)]
        IstioGateway[Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Authorino[Authorino<br/>AuthZ Provider]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>modelregistry.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates/manages| RESTProxy
    Operator -->|creates/manages| GRPCServer
    Operator -->|creates| IstioResources[Istio Resources<br/>Gateway, VirtualService,<br/>DestinationRule, AuthPolicy]

    ExternalClient[External Client] -->|HTTPS/443| IstioGateway
    IstioGateway -->|routes to| EnvoyProxy
    IstioGateway -->|validates auth| Authorino

    EnvoyProxy -->|mTLS| RESTProxy
    EnvoyProxy -->|mTLS| GRPCServer

    GRPCServer -->|PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>TLS optional| Database

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS| KubeRBACProxy

    Operator -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style KubeRBACProxy fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style RESTProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style GRPCServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style EnvoyProxy fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333
    style Database fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style IstioGateway fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Authorino fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
